title: This updated NSFW version of 'Back To The Future Part Two' proves that 2015 sucks
text:
We've all failed them and ourselves in making our present suck.
'Back To The Future Day' is rolling around next week, and with that College Humor decided to update Marty and Doc's trip to 2015 to reflect what it would be like if they actually arrived in the 'future' of today.
The result proves just how awful we all are. Let's just try and make flying cars, hoverboards and clean energy happen in the next 30 years, alright?
Via College Humor
